And when the apostles opened the tomb on the third day they found it empty. The holy body had been assumed into heaven in glory. And they fell on their faces and worshiped YHWH with fear and exceeding joy.
Then a great light and heavenly fragrance filled the place. The Virgin appeared to the apostles transfigured in glory saying: “Rejoice my beloved sons. I have been taken up to my Son and your Lord. I go to prepare a place for you and intercede for you before the throne of YHWH.”
