Then the holy Virgin blessed each apostle individually and said: “Peace be with you my children. I go to my Son who has called me. Remain in love and unity until we meet again in the kingdom of YHWH.”
And when the hour of her departure drew near, the apostles were gathered from the ends of the earth upon clouds by the power of YHWH and brought before her. And she spoke to them final words of comfort, blessing, and eternal hope.

